Vendored into metal-SingleCell (rather than taken as a runtime dependency) to keep the
dependency footprint minimal; the file is used unmodified. metal-SingleCell adapts its
output at call sites (over-build + self-prepend in metasinglecell.neighbors) but does not
modify this vendored source.

Changes to the vendored file: none.
